                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/C:/Users/patscully/Desktop/My%20Stuff/workspace/publication/mediterranean_cuisine/topics/task/Italian_meatballs.dita" xtrc="cmd:4;56:22">Deglaze the pan with a splash of white wine, then add the tinned tomatoes along with the basil, oregano and some seasoning.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/C:/Users/patscully/Desktop/My%20Stuff/workspace/publication/mediterranean_cuisine/topics/task/Italian_meatballs.dita" xtrc="step:5;58:19">
                <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/C:/Users/patscully/Desktop/My%20Stuff/workspace/publication/mediterranean_cuisine/topics/task/Italian_meatballs.dita" xtrc="cmd:5;59:22">Throw in the olives if using and let the sauce simmer for 5-10 minutes to reduce and thicken.
                </cmd>
